幣1,000元。\r\n中　　華　　民　　國　　111 　年　　8 　　月　　15　　日\r\n                                書記官  張宏賓","JFULLPDF":"https://data.judicial.gov.tw/jdg/api/JDocFile/TCDV/111%2c%e9%87%8d%e8%a8%b4%2c433%2c20220815%2c1/pdf"},"JID":"TCDV,111,重訴,433,20220815,1","JYEAR":"111","JCASE":"重訴","JNO":"433","JDATE":"20220815","JTITLE":"履行契約等"}